So a few angles you can think about or questions you can ask him might be: What kinds of questions come up the most often besides just the therapist one? Are there patterns in the kind of information people are looking for? Also, does he imagine that the app would be a space where people can not only find info but also connect with each other or share their own resources? Basically, is it more of a directory or is it also a community hub?

